Context:
Toronto has 55 hospitals and is the fourth largest medical community in North America. George Brown College offers clinical placements for students in some of Canada's busiest hospitals and clinics, as well as community-focused environments. The Centre for Health Sciences provides customized programs for health care professionals. Some companies that George Brown College has worked with include those listed on their website. Students in the Sally Horsfall School of Nursing have opportunities for clinical placements in hospital, long-term, and community healthcare settings across the Toronto area.
